zserio.runtime.creator

Class ZserioTreeCreator

  • java.lang.Object
    • zserio.runtime.creator.ZserioTreeCreator

  • public final class ZserioTreeCreator
extends java.lang.Object
    Creator for zserio objects. It allows to build zserio object tree defined by the given type info (see -withTypeInfoCode).
